===========================================================
Package: CPSDefault 3.60.0
===========================================================
First release built by: div at: 2007-03-26T20:46:45
SVN Tag: https://svn.nuxeo.org/pub/CPS3/products/CPSDefault/tags/3.60.0
Build from: https://svn.nuxeo.org/pub/CPS3/products/CPSDefault/trunk@51414

Requires
~~~~~~~~
-
New features
~~~~~~~~~~~~
- Added a target section selection for #1807 
  "Provide a mean to publish all the contents of a tree structure in one go".
Bug fixes
~~~~~~~~~
- Fixed #1814 "Misconfiguration of last_login_time default value in members
  schema" by improving the logged_in.py script.
- Fixed root creation when no portal_type nor meta_type is specified.
- Removed rss.js which is not used by the RSS feeds produced by
  CPSPortlets, it was used by CPSBoxes.
- Updated Spanish translation thanks to Jesús Martín.
- Translated the "Breaking News" and "Latest Published" portlets' titles.
New internal features
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- 

===========================================================
Package: CPSDefault 3.59.0
===========================================================
First release built by: div at: 2007-03-14T12:22:23
SVN Tag: https://svn.nuxeo.org/pub/CPS3/products/CPSDefault/tags/3.59.0
Build from: https://svn.nuxeo.org/pub/CPS3/products/CPSDefault/trunk@51329

Requires
~~~~~~~~
-
New features
~~~~~~~~~~~~
- Added the possibility to create any objects at the root of a CPS site
  (for example Zope objects such as cache managers) by specifying them in
  profiles/default/roots.xml. Previously it was limited to only CPS objects.
- #1800 : Implement faster portlet lookup.
- Accessibility improvement: Added alt attribute for ImageWidget and
  PhotoWidget.
Bug fixes
~~~~~~~~~
- Added a permission check on the recursivePublish method.
- fix: traceback on reindexFolderContentPositions when not authorized.
- Improved the accessibility usefulness and explanations.
New internal features
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- 

