===========================================================
Package: CPSDefault 3.57.0
===========================================================
First release built by: gracinet at: 2007-02-06T14:44:23
SVN Tag: https://svn.nuxeo.org/pub/CPS3/products/CPSDefault/tags/3.57.0
Build from: https://svn.nuxeo.org/pub/CPS3/products/CPSDefault/trunk@50983

Requires
~~~~~~~~
-
New features
~~~~~~~~~~~~
- Enhancement #1807 : Provide a mean to publish all the contents of a tree
  structure in one go.
Bug fixes
~~~~~~~~~
- Fixed #1806 "Fields with errors have their error message not associated them
  and too far below".
- Fix: modified date on folder contents are wrong and not sorted correctly.
  now display proxy.modified vs doc.modified
- Can run without ExternalEditor
New internal features
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- metafactory's driven replay_profiles start by reinstalling the base profile
- doctest doc/developer/metafactory.txt doesn't depend on python-ldap anymore.

===========================================================
Package: CPSDefault 3.56.5
===========================================================
First release built by: div at: 2007-01-16T18:02:17
SVN Tag: https://svn.nuxeo.org/pub/CPS3/products/CPSDefault/tags/3.56.5
Build from: https://svn.nuxeo.org/pub/CPS3/products/CPSDefault/trunk@50830

Requires
~~~~~~~~
-
New features
~~~~~~~~~~~~
-
Bug fixes
~~~~~~~~~
- Granted the permission "Access inactive portal content" to the Manager,
  SectionManager and SectionReviewer in Sections so that those roles are able to
  access contents with expiration_date in the future and effective_date in the
  past while using the catalog navigation, cf.
  CPSDefault.utils.getCatalogFolderContents.
New internal features
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- 

