  widget was not activated to enforce the range.
- Made the Subjects be outputted sorted.
- The translations for the message "description_logout_success" had been lost
  for the fr, en and es locales.
- Ordered languages in the CPSDefault Site creation form and checked Spanish and
  Euskara by default too since their support is complete.
New internal features
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
