Bug fixes
~~~~~~~~~
-
New internal features
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- made content_status_modify more generic to be more reusable in custom
  projects

===========================================================
Package: CPSDefault 3.47.0
===========================================================
First release built by: ben at: 2006-09-28T17:39:38
SVN Tag: https://svn.nuxeo.org/pub/CPS3/products/CPSDefault/tags/3.47.0
Build from: https://svn.nuxeo.org/pub/CPS3/products/CPSDefault/trunk@49250

Requires:
~~~~~~~~~
-
New features:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- simpler logout process
Bug fixes:
~~~~~~~~~~
- Missing ACL on members confirm password field.
- Removed duplicate CSS definitions + added better default styling for buttons.
- KeyError 'logger' in upgrade steps.
- Removed display of error stack trace on error page for error_type == 'NotFound'.
- #1748: folder contents sometimes breaks with NameError 'proxy_creator'
- fix: use_catalog_for_folder_contents raise site error on folder listing
New internal features:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- Leverage new 'View status history' permission.

