** CPSDefault V3.37.1 [R1 build 2005/11/08-16:53 by fguillaume]
** SVN URL: https://svn.nuxeo.org/pub/CPSDefault/trunk Revision: 29274
Requires:
~~~~~~~~~
-
New features:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~
-
Bug fixes:
~~~~~~~~~~
- Made the CSS validity link, in the conformance statement portlet, explicitly
  ask for validation against the CSS 2.1 spec, otherwise the W3C CSS validator
  tries to validate against the CSS 2 spec.
- Fix SpecialUser API failure #1113
New internal features:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
